    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Search the connected Google Sheet. Each row contains avatar voice information, including a \"description\" column that describes the voice type, tone, and style (e.g., \"20s, casual sports attire, enthusiastic tone with a competitive edge\"). The input \"Avatar Style\" may describe similar traits in different words. Perform a semantic match — focus on overall meaning, tone, age group, and personality. Case-insensitive. Return the row that most closely aligns in meaning, even if the wording is different.\n\ngiven Avatar Style : {{ $('Split Out1').item.json.avatarStyle }}\n\nThis is an exemple of structure format , return 1 per item\n\n{\n  \"response\": [\n    {\n      \"row_number\": 2,\n      \"Name\": \"Linda\",\n      \"template id\": \"Maroal_CasualLook_public\",\n      \"voice id\": \"3ec2466e4d2847a88e9c10b8cf58e1cb\",\n      \"description\": \"Young Woman\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"row_number\": 5,\n      \"Name\": \"George\",\n      \"template id\": \"Mark_FitnessCoach_public\",\n      \"voice id\": \"e6baf4892d344b61a7033502899208ff\",\n      \"description\": \"Middle-aged Man\"\n    },\n    {...}\n  ]\n}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
